movie.title: Medicine Man
movie.description_intro: An eccentric scientist working for a large drug company is working on a research project in the Amazon jungle. He sends for a research assistant and a gas chromatograph because he's close to a cure for cancer. When the assistant turns out to be a "mere woman", he rejects her help. Meanwhile, the bulldozers get closer to the area in which they are conducting research, and they eventually learn to work together, and begin to fall in love.

movies.title: Journey to the West: The Demons Strike Back
movies.title_english: Journey to the West: The Demons Strike Back
movies.title_long: Journey to the West: The Demons Strike Back (2017)
movies.summary: Tang Monk brings three disciples on a journey to the West. On the outside, everything seems harmonious. However, tension is present beneath the surface, and their hearts and minds are not in agreement. After a series of demon-capturing events, the monk and his disciples gain mutual understanding of each others' hardships and unease. Finally, they resolve their inner conflict and work together to become an all-conquering, demon-exorcising team.

movies.title: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides
movies.title_english: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides
movies.title_long: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides (2011)
movies.summary: Captain Jack Sparrow (Johnny Depp) crosses paths with a woman from his past, Angelica (Penélope Cruz), and he's not sure if it's love, or if she's a ruthless con artist who's using him to find the fabled Fountain of Youth. When she forces him aboard the Queen Anne's Revenge, the ship of the formidable pirate Blackbeard (Ian McShane), Jack finds himself on an unexpected adventure in which he doesn't know who to fear more: Blackbeard or the woman from his past.

movies.title: Rabbit School - Guardians of the Golden Egg
movies.title_english: Rabbit School - Guardians of the Golden Egg
movies.title_long: Rabbit School - Guardians of the Golden Egg (2017)
movies.summary: Max, a cheeky city rabbit, winds up in an Easter rabbit school where time seems to have stood still. Thanks to training lessons from mysterious Madame Hermione and with the help of cute rabbit girl Emmi, he not only learns about the secret techniques of Easter bunnies but even more about himself when they have to fight a clever fox family that has been scheming to take over Easter.

movies.title: Duck Duck Goose
movies.summary: Peng is a freewheeling bachelor goose who'd rather do anything than practice for the upcoming migration. He thinks he's better than everyone else and spends his time attempting crazy stunts at even crazier speeds. In one such stunt, Peng flies too near the ground, hits a flock of ducklings and separates brother and sister, Chao and Chi, from the rest. In this unlikely meeting, Peng will begin a journey that will break his wing and nearly break his heart as he grows to understand the power of unconditional love in the form of two ducklings, who likewise grow to see him as the best father they could ever have.
